By editing /etc/polkit-1/localauthority/50-local.d/com.ubuntu.enable-hibernate.pkla


Add this to it if you want hibernation

[Enable Hibernate]
Identity=unix-user:*
Action=org.freedesktop.upower.hibernate
ResultActive=yes

Or remove it if you wanna disable it


Via http://www.howtogeek.com/113923/how-to-re-enable-hibernate-in-ubuntu-12.04/
